data.output: The empire was growing stronger, their fierce leader implementing new rules to his citizens daily and ensuring he had eyes all over the place to ensure they comply with the new rules. The people of Augmentia, unbeknownst to them, had been born on the island and brainwashed into the ways of the land. When a citizen of Augmentia reached the age of 20, they were enlisted into a type of military boot camp where they had to comply with strict instructions and a gruelling regime of work, exercise, and weapons training. Those who did not comply with instructions, or tried to rebel against the bootcamps leaders, were never seen again by their families.
